title: Advances In Genome Biology And Technology
description: Advances in Genome Biology and Technology (AGBT) will celebrate 20 years as the preeminent genome science and technology conference where top global researchers, leaders and innovators meet to announce new discoveries, cutting edge breakthroughs and to collaborate. As a recognized cornerstone for the genomics research community, AGBT provides an outstanding forum for exchanging information about the latest advances in DNA sequencing technologies, experimental and analytical approaches for genomic studies, and their myriad applications.

title: Cyber Risk Strategies to Improve Organizational Resilience and Value
description: Join us for the CDW Protect SummIT on "Cyber Risk Strategies to Improve Organizational Resilience and Value" – presented in partnership with CIO, CSO, Computerworld and Network World – where we’ll bring together experts who are savvy to these questions, challenges, solutions and more.
